      answer: "Install My Kitchen is a specialist independent kitchen fitter based in Coventry, serving all Coventry postcodes and surrounding Warwickshire. We install kitchens from all major retailers including Wren, Howdens, Magnet and IKEA.",
      takeaways: ["Independent kitchen fitter based in Coventry", "All CV postcodes covered", "We fit all major retailer brands", "Call 07399 651836 to book your survey"],
      body: `<h2>Independent Kitchen Fitter in Coventry</h2><p>Install My Kitchen is a specialist kitchen fitting company based in Coundon, Coventry. We provide an independent kitchen installation service to homeowners across all Coventry postcodes — from Earlsdon and Canley in the west to Binley and Wyken in the east, and from Coundon and Radford in the north to Finham and Stivichall in the south.</p><h2>Why Choose an Independent Kitchen Fitter?</h2><p>Choosing an independent kitchen fitter means choosing a service that works for you rather than for a retailer. We are not commissioned by any kitchen brand, we do not have installation quotas to meet, and our only measure of success is a kitchen that is fitted to the highest standard and a client who is completely satisfied. This independence gives us the freedom to take the time a quality installation requires.</p><h2>Retailers We Fit in Coventry</h2><p>We install kitchens purchased from all major UK retailers, including Wren, Howdens, Magnet, IKEA, Wickes, B&Q, Benchmarx, DIY Kitchens, and many more. We also install premium brands including Häcker, Nobilia, Mereway, Neptune and deVOL. If you have bought it, we can fit it.</p><h2>Booking Your Kitchen Fitter in Coventry</h2><p>The first step is a pre-installation survey at your home. Our surveyor checks your room against your kitchen plan, assesses all services and room conditions, and provides a fixed installation quote. The survey costs £195 and is credited back against your installation when you confirm your date. Call 07399 651836 or book online.</p>`,
